Consumer Side

@KafkaListener → Listens for messages from Kafka topics.

ConsumerFactory → Creates Kafka Consumer instances.

DefaultKafkaConsumerFactory → Default implementation that creates Kafka consumers.

ConcurrentKafkaListenerContainerFactory → Creates listener containers used by @KafkaListener.

StringDeserializer → Converts Kafka key bytes into String.

JacksonJsonDeserializer → Converts JSON messages into Java objects.

GROUP_ID_CONFIG → Identifies the consumer group.

groupId → Consumers with the same group-id share messages.

BOOTSTRAP_SERVERS_CONFIG → Kafka broker address used by the consumer.

addTrustedPackages() → Specifies which packages are allowed for JSON deserialization.

OrderEvent.class → Tells the deserializer to convert JSON into an OrderEvent object.